  Mint Arch Linux — Rolling Arch Linux with Security Tools + KDE Plasma
  ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  Quick commands:
    mint-installer      — Install Mint Arch Linux to disk
    mint-tools-setup    — Install security tool categories
    mint-update         — Safe system update (with snapshot)
    mint-hardware       — Auto-detect & install GPU/CPU drivers
    mint-privacy        — Privacy & firewall hardening
    mint-health         — System health dashboard
    mint-snapshot       — Manage Btrfs snapshots & rollbacks
    mint-gaming         — Install Steam, Wine, Proton & gaming tweaks
    mint-setup-aur      — Install paru (AUR helper)

  All tools sourced from official Arch Linux repositories.

